{"tid":2330043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港市民的憤怒與痛苦：「我要上班」成為訴求","createTime":"2020-12-17T16:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T03:02:50.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d024d1776917c53dfc07ad343a7a253debad9d","tid":2330043,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"昨天（5日），香港一批激進分子發起所謂「三罷」（即罷工、罷課、罷市）行動。從清晨開始，他們就流竄各區破壞全港交通。從港鐵到巴士，從機場到市區，無一倖免，全港交通大癱瘓，令上班、出行的市民和旅客嚴重受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=c5vo8p/ctp-vzntr/ELYhWOgNDyoWPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dc5vo8p%2Fctp-vzntr%2FELYhWOgNDyoWPS.jpg&h=077707c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是5日上午8點多的港鐵地圖，標紅點的車站都被迫停止服務，而且這些車站幾乎都是人流量大的站<br />\n<br />\n為了不讓港鐵正常運行、不讓上班族正常上班，暴力分子無所不用其極，醜態百出。他們躺着、趴着，用自己的身體或是用行李箱等物品阻擋在車門處，不讓車門關上，阻撓列車開動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1fbrrfr/ctp-vzntr/ELYhWPW2ot6o02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1fbrrfr%2Fctp-vzntr%2FELYhWPW2ot6o02.jpg&h=2072ceaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至還有示威者將自行車、手推車等障礙物放到了路軌上，有列車在行駛中撞到了這些障礙物，險象環生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=1soe887/ctp-vzntr/ELYhWuhTW5NN0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1soe887%2Fctp-vzntr%2FELYhWuhTW5NN0J.jpg&h=874f890b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算擠上了巴士，上班的路途還是路漫漫其修遠兮，因為有幾十條路段都是示威者用水馬圍欄、鐵欄杆等雜物堵住了，車輛無法通行，交通異常擁堵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2a4rk96/ctp-vzntr/ELYhWvCVaHPeZ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2a4rk96%2Fctp-vzntr%2FELYhWvCVaHPeZ0.jpg&h=4347d2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上班之路如此困難，香港的上班族們輕言放棄了嗎？沒有！他們踏平坎坷成大道，斗罷艱險又出發。巴士站里，上班族們在烈日下井然有序地排隊等車去上班；還有人乾脆坐上了「11路公共汽車」&mdash;&mdash;走路去上班。更有白領模樣的上班族主動幫警察清理路障，讓車輛可以順利通行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5N6beUu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5N6beUu.gif&h=4c656ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有香港市民在接受媒體採訪時說：「我的訴求就是想上班。」對於香港的上班族來說，堅持上班，就是向示威者宣戰，表達愛港愛國的一種最直接的態度!不論這一小撮亂港辱國者再出何招數，他們註定徒勞，因為愛國始終是中國人民精神底蘊里的最大公約數。"},{"pid":"9303b0141beb90d3555196176767225be66becc4","tid":2330043,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">黎字派 <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"57a946e1e975f447913eca832432307c1f8c25fc","tid":2330043,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"黎生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e22b0705aae4e1d37cf91a747471bd7f586ab10","tid":2330043,"uid":41957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為愛國始終是中國人民精神底蘊里的最大公約數。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為<del>愛國</del><span class=\"red\">返工</span>始終是中國人民精神底蘊里的最大公約數。"},{"pid":"79f7a1367caa08d64c92159fc64c57cfafe98dc3","tid":2330043,"uid":337444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"黎字頭全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09c714531de76455c627e2b350f0d89fe293765","tid":2330043,"uid":165282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"🙏🏻"},{"pid":"90fc5e804dc02d83d51facf0c0020349f7998238","tid":2330043,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58801636fc62a71976b3f0474fed60c3663f4c6","tid":2330043,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"畜同奴嘅基本素質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}